{
  "stem": "19969.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 137.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She described it, although, in her words, she was the first one in there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In her book, which was a biography of her, she writes that a German SS general met her at the main gate and escorted-- sent a lieutenant to escort her through the camp.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Hell, there wasn't an SS general within 100 miles of Dachau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The commandant was a colonel, but he had long since gone before we ever got there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But that was her story anyway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But she admits-- she said that she had some words with an officer from the 45 Division, which was me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she claims that she-- I grabbed her by the shoulder.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Well, I didn't touch the woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I did order her out, but I never laid a hand on her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That's her story anyway.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But the strange part of it is, it was never mentioned.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "In the lengthy investigation, the 42nd never mentioned her presence.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And-- but they were there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They took some prisoners.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But they did not-- were not the first there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they were not the ones who liberated the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "That's what they claim now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This record-- they admit they weren't there till 3:30 that afternoon in the sworn testimony.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they admit-- well, nobody admits killing those guards.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just-- one of the sergeants said, well, I-- they're all standing there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somebody starts shooting them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They killed all of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at that point, they decided they better get out of there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because my men were right on the scene.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My men saw the shooting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never had an opportunity, you see, because I was gone a couple days later.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- you know, a lot of my men are still alive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were there.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
